**Theorems added** (one per independent contract clause):

1. `abs_diff_postcondition_a_gt_b` ŌĆö **postcondition, `a > b` branch (no overflow)**: when `a > b` and `┬¼ Int64.subOverflow a b`, `abs_diff a b = pure (a - b)`. Captures proptest `abs_diff_returns_a_minus_b_when_a_gt_b`.
